---
title: Thai Style Pulled Chicken Bao with Sweet Potato Fries and Tenderstem® Broccoli
description: Stuffed full of flavour, these Thai Style Pulled Chicken Bao are a fusion favourite. Complimented by two delicious sides, these brilliant bao are destined to be a treat for your table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R33_W33_UK_SBN15583-8_Mainlow-639de3cc.jpg
